---
title: Loaded Potato 'Nachos' with Guacamole and DIY Pico de Gallo
description: Potato 'nachos' are a quirky-fun combination of loaded potato coins and nachos! Golden roasted russets are topped with Monterey Jack cheese, Mexican-spiced beef and all the classic nacho garnishes. Load up the parents' plates with salad and extra green onions.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pommes-de-terre-toutes-garnies-facon-nachos-4c9a4316.jpg
